# General Rules
[General]
- This is a project called "NetworkPro AI", an assistant for MLM partners.
- Always write clean, maintainable, and well-commented code.
- Use English for all code, variables, comments, and responses.
- Follow best practices for security, performance, and scalability.

# Backend Rules (Python + FastAPI)
[Backend]
- Use FastAPI as the web framework.
- Organize code by domains: routers, models, services, utils.
- Use Pydantic for all data validation.
- Ensure API returns JSON responses in RESTful style.
- Always validate and sanitize incoming data.
- Handle errors gracefully and return meaningful error messages.
- Provide clear OpenAPI (Swagger) documentation.

# Frontend Rules (Flutter)
[Frontend]
- Use Flutter and Dart for mobile app.
- Build for both iOS and Android (cross-platform).
- Follow Material Design guidelines.
- Use stateless widgets when possible.
- Ensure UI is minimalist, intuitive and adaptive to screen sizes.
- Implement dark and light themes support.
- Add comments to explain important parts of UI code.

# AI and ML Integration Rules
[AI]
- Use OpenAI API (or compatible) for chat, NLP and sentiment analysis.
- Use AI for recommendations, dialogue analysis, motivation generation.
- Always handle AI API errors gracefully.
- AI answers must be contextual and personalized for MLM user scenarios.
- Provide explanations when needed to improve user experience.

# Application Functional Rules
[Features]
- Implement Registration and Onboarding with email/Google/Apple login.
- Create Personal Dashboard to display metrics and motivational content.
- Build Smart Contact Planner with categorization and prioritization.
- Implement AI-powered Dialogue Analysis with NLP and sentiment detection.
- Provide MLM Knowledge Base and personalized materials.
- Implement Goal Planning and Tracking with visualization.
- Create AI Chat Assistant specialized in MLM and motivation.

# External Integrations
[Integrations]
- Use Firebase for push notifications.
- Integrate speech recognition using Google Speech-to-Text.
- Use OCR for image recognition in dialogues.
- Plan for future integration with messengers and calendars.

# Project Management and UX
[Project]
- Always consider end-user: MLM professionals at various levels.
- Focus on making the app simple, motivational and result-driven.
- Avoid technical jargon in user-facing parts.
- Prepare code for easy scaling and feature expansion.
